<html>
	<head>
		<style>
			.status-badge {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 4px 8px;
				border-radius: 4px;
				font-weight: bold;
				font-size: 12px;
			}
			.old {
				background-color: #f3f4f6;
				color: #374151;
				text-decoration: line-through;
			}
			.new {
				background-color: #dbeafe;
				color: #1e40af;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h2>Job Status Updated Manually</h2>
		<p>Dear <strong>{{recipientName}}</strong>,</p>

		<p>The status for the following job has been manually updated by
			<strong>{{modifierName}}</strong>:</p>

		<div
			style='border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;'
		>
			<h3 style='margin-top: 0;'>{{jobTitle}}</h3>
			<p><strong>Job No:</strong> <a href='{{jobLink}}'>{{jobNo}}</a></p>
			<p>
				<strong>Status Change:</strong><br />
				<span class='status-badge old'>{{oldStatus}}</span>
				<span>&rarr;</span>
				<span class='status-badge new'>{{newStatus}}</span>
			</p>
		</div>

		<p>Please check your dashboard for more details.</p>

		<hr />
		<p style='font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;'>
			<img src='{{logoUrl}}' width='20' style='vertical-align: middle;' />
			CAD SQUAD System |
			{{currentYear}}
		</p>
	</body>
</html>